@startuml
title 目标层活动图（正演、反演、异步生命周期）

' ========== 正演流程 ==========
|User|
start
:User submits model\n(YAML/CLI/API);
|Interface Layer|
:Input Validator\n语法、字段检查;
if (Valid?) then (no)
    :Return error to user;
    stop
else (yes)
    |Model Layer|
    :Hierarchy Manager\n继承链解析与版本控制;
    :Conflict Detector\n物理不自洽检测;
    if (Conflict?) then (yes)
        |Interface Layer|
        :Notify user of conflicts;
        stop
    else (no)
        :Completeness Checker\n计算链路完整性验证;
        if (Incomplete?) then (yes)
            |Interface Layer|
            :Notify user of missing steps;
            stop
        else (no)
            |Model Layer|
            :Compute Runtime\n资源调度与缓存;
            :Physics Engine\n综合 SourceModel, BackgroundModel,\nTransmissionModel 执行仿真;
            :Generate TargetHistogram\n(内存对象);
            |Data Layer|
            :FITS/HDF5 I/O Manager\n序列化为标准 FITS 文件包;
            :Observables Interface\n写入层间交换目录;
            :Create .forward_ready sentinel;
            |Observables Layer|
            :Receive forward products;
            |Interface Layer|
            :Result Presenter\n(optional status query);
            stop
        endif
    endif
endif

' ========== 异步任务生命周期（正演/反演通用） ==========
|Model Layer|
fork
    :Compute Runtime\nTask queued;
    :Resource admission check;
    if (Resources sufficient?) then (yes)
        :Execute task;
        while (Task running?) is (running)
            :Update status → executing;
        endwhile (done)
        if (Success?) then (yes)
            :Status → completed;
        else (failure)
            :Status → error;
            |Interface Layer|
            :Notify user of error;
        endif
    else (no)
        :Reject or defer;\nStatus → rejected/queued;
        |Interface Layer|
        :Notify user of resource shortage;
    endif
end fork

' ========== 反演流程 ==========
|Observables Layer|
start
:Place .inverse_ready sentinel\nand data products;
|Data Layer|
:Observables Interface\ndetect ready signal;
if (.error sentinel exists?) then (yes)
    |Data Layer|
    :Read error code and summary;
    |Interface Layer|
    :Present error to user;
    stop
else (no)
    :FITS/HDF5 I/O Manager\nparse to TargetHistogram (memory);
    |Model Layer|
    :Compute Runtime\nassign resources;
    :Parameter Estimator\nMCMC / nested sampling / MLE\nusing priors from Source, Background, Transmission;
    :Statistics Evaluator\ncompute χ², residuals, confidence intervals,\nupdate model instances;
    |Interface Layer|
    :Result Presenter\nformat reports (JSON/YAML/Markdown/plots);
    stop
endif

@enduml
